	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />没错～<20_2 arg="4" /><delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我们已经选出了几种备选礼物，<delay20 />
