	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />制作过程中<20_2 arg="3" />我们还可以聊聊天<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
喝杯茶吃点蛋糕休息一下<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="HappyFlower" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />嗯，<delay8 />
