<20_3 arg="5" /><20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然决定好了，<delay20 />
我们就赶快开始准备吧！</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />让我们拿出真本事，<20_2 arg="4" />大显身手一番吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="IdeaBulb" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />对了！<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />要不要来我家<delay20 />一起准备呀？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我最近<delay8 />买了个非常厉害的搅拌器，<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
想请你们<delay8 />也来看看<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />哇～<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />
我也正好<delay20 />买了最新款的橡胶料理铲哦～<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Grin" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />它的弹性远超至今为止的其他款式！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />正好可以让你们也试用一下，<delay20 />
我把它带过去哦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Nodding" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />光是把玻璃杯高高叠起，<delay20 /><20_2 arg="7" /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />
就能营造出一种奢华的感觉呢。<pageBreak /><20_3 arg="5" /><20_3 arg="7" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />不过<delay8 />要准备这么多玻璃杯的话，<delay40 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />只靠我家里的那些，<delay20 />
可能不太够<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Assent" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />我也把<20_2 arg="4" />家里的玻璃杯<delay20 />
