	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">哇～<delay8 />感觉真不错呢～<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Love" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />能在那种环境里<delay20 />读自己喜欢的书，<delay8 />
