<anim id="Blushing" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />格外有情调哦～<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />，<delay8 />
你有没有什么<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />特别钟爱的环境呀～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />要说<20_2 arg="3" />我的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我还是喜欢在漫天繁星之下<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />
