	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />哇～<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />听起来真棒～<delay40 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />我要不要也试一次看看呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />可以的话，<20_2 arg="3" />要不要一起试一试呀？<delay40 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />在星空下<delay8 />办个读书会！<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Pardon" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />哇！<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />真是个好主意！<delay40 />
<anim id="Restless" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />不过<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 />要是看不到星星的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />该怎么办呀？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />真遇上那种情况<20_2 arg="3" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="60" />
