<anim id="OhGeez" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />那就变成<anim id="Worried" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />普通的茶会了呢。</message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />所以我们一起祈祷<20_2 arg="3" /><delay8 />能够看见漂亮的星空吧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />详细事宜，<delay20 />
就等下次再讨论。<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />我明白了。<delay40 />
