	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />谢谢你～<20_2 arg="4" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />话说回来，<delay8 />我从刚才开始就有点在意<delay40 />
