<anim id="QuestionMark" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />你以前就是这样说话的吗？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyFlower" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />呵呵！<20_2 arg="3" />你注意到了吗？<delay40 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你<delay8 />果然很敏锐！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />改变说话方式，<delay20 />感觉自己的想法也会受影响，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />还挺不错的呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />呀，<20_2 arg="4" /><delay20 />原来是这样啊？<delay40 />
