<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Hesitate" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />那个～<delay40 />
我可不可以<delay20 />也模仿一下<delay8 />
